INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES (1391,'_transient_aopro_explain','<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'default\'>\n    <div id=\"aoprocontainer\">\n      <div id=\"aoprotxt\">\n      <h2>Add more power to Autoptimize with Pro!</h2>\n        <p>As a user of Autoptimize you understand <strong>the importance of having a fast site</strong>. Autoptimize Pro is a premium Power-Up extending AO by adding <strong>image optimization, CDN, automatic critical CSS rules generation and page caching</strong>. Additionally AOPro also provides extra <strong>&quot;booster&quot; options</strong> e.g. to further <strong>delay JavaScript or part of the HTML</strong>. All is part of one handy subscription to make your site <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">get better Google PageSpeed Insights scores</span>! And <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/#aopro_reviews\" target=\"_blank\">customers ❤️ AOPro</a>!</p>\n        <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n        <a href=\"https://checkout.freemius.com/mode/dialog/plugin/10906/plan/18508/?currency=auto\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"aoprobuy\" class=\"button button-primary\">\n            <p id=\"cta\">Buy your subscription now!</p>\n            <p>Monthly price starting from 5&euro;/$</p>\n        </a>\n        <p>Or have a look at <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> for more info and screenshots!</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"aoproimg\">\n        <img src=\"https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_264/https://autoptimize.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/total-sale-264x300.png\" width=\"264px\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'nl\'>\n    <div id=\"aoprocontainer\">\n      <div id=\"aoprotxt\">\n    <h2>Maak je site nog sneller met Autoptimize Pro!</h2>\n      <p>Als gebruiker van Autoptimize begrijp je het <strong>belang van een snelle website</strong>. Autoptimize Pro is een premium Power-Up die AO uitbreidt door <strong>beeldoptimalisatie, CDN, automatisch genereren van kritische CSS-regels en paginacaching</strong> toe te voegen. Daarnaast biedt AOPro ook extra <strong>&quot;booster&quot;-opties</strong> zoals het <strong>uitgesteld uitvoeren van JavaScript of van een deel van de HTML</strong>. Alles zit in één handig abonnement om je site nog <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">beter te laten scoren op Google PageSpeed Insights</span>! En <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/#aopro_reviews\" target=\"_blank\">klanten ❤️  AOPro</a>!</p>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n        <a href=\"https://checkout.freemius.com/mode/dialog/plugin/10906/plan/18508/?currency=auto\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"aoprobuy\" class=\"button button-primary\">\n            <p id=\"cta\">Koop nu je abonnement!</p>\n            <p>Maandelijkse prijs vanaf 5&euro;/$</p>\n        </a>\n        <p>Of kijk op <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> voor meer info en screenshots!</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"aoproimg\">\n        <img src=\"https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_264/https://autoptimize.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/total-sale-264x300.png\" width=\"264px\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'fr\'> \n    <div id=\"aoprocontainer\">\n      <div id=\"aoprotxt\">\n      <h2>Rendez votre site encore plus rapide avec Autoptimize Pro !</h2>\n        <p>En tant qu\'utilisateur d\'Autoptimize, vous comprenez <strong>l\'importance d\'avoir un site rapide</strong>. Autoptimize Pro est un &quot;Power-Up&quot; payant &eacute;tendant AO en ajoutant <strong>l\'optimisation d\'images, le CDN, la g&eacute;n&eacute;ration automatique de r&egrave;gles CSS critiques et la mise en cache des pages</strong>. En plus AOPro fournisse des <strong>options de &quot;booster&quot;</strong> par example pour <strong>retarder l\'execution de JavaScript ou d\'une partie du HTML</strong>. Le tout est compris dans un seul abonnement pratique pour <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">am&eacute;liorer le score Google PageSpeed Insights</span> de votre site! Et les <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/#aopro_reviews\" target=\"_blank\">clients ❤️  AOPro</a> ! </p>\n        <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n        <a href=\"https://checkout.freemius.com/mode/dialog/plugin/10906/plan/18508/?currency=auto\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"aoprobuy\" class=\"button button-primary\">\n            <p id=\"cta\">Achetez votre abonnement maintenant !</p>\n            <p>Prix mensuel &agrave; partir de 5&euro;/$</p>\n        </a>\n        <p>Ou jetez un &oelig;il &agrave; <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> pour plus d\'informations et des captures d\'&eacute;cran&nbsp;!</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"aoproimg\">\n        <img src=\"https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_264/https://autoptimize.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/total-sale-264x300.png\" width=\"264px\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'es\'>\n    <div id=\"aoprocontainer\">\n      <div id=\"aoprotxt\">\n      <h2>&iexcl;Acelere su sitio con Autoptimize Pro!</h2>\n        <p>Como usuario de Autoptimize, comprende la <strong>importancia de un sitio r&aacute;pido</strong>. Autoptimize Pro es un &quot;Power-Up&quot; premium que extiende AO agregando <strong> optimizaci&oacute;n de im&aacute;genes, CDN, generaci&oacute;n autom&aacute;tica de reglas CSS cr&iacute;ticas y almacenamiento en cach&eacute; de p&aacute;ginas</strong>. Adem&aacute;s, AOPro ofrece <strong>opciones &quot;booster&quot;</strong>  para por ejemplo <strong>ralentizar la ejecuci&oacute;n de JavaScript o parte del HTML</strong>. &iexcl;Todo est&aacute; incluido en una c&oacute;moda suscripci&oacute;n para <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">mejorar la puntuaci&oacute;n de Google PageSpeed ​​​​Insights</span> de su sitio! Y <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/#aopro_reviews\" target=\"_blank\">clientes ❤️ AOPro</a> ! </p>\n        <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n        <a href=\"https://checkout.freemius.com/mode/dialog/plugin/10906/plan/18508/?currency=auto\" target=\"_blank\" id=\"aoprobuy\" class=\"button button-primary\">\n            <p id=\"cta\">&iexcl;Compra tu suscripci&oacute;n ahora!</p>\n            <p>Precio mensual desde 5&euro;/$</p>\n        </a>\n        <p>&iexcl;O eche un vistazo a <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> para obtener m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n y capturas de pantalla!</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"aoproimg\">\n        <img src=\"https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/to_webp,q_glossy,ret_img,w_264/https://autoptimize.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/total-sale-264x300.png\" width=\"264px\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n','no');
