INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES (1412,'_transient_ao3_ccss_explain','<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'default\'>\n    <h2>Improve performance with critical CSS</h2>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden\">\n    <div style=\"width:68%;float:left\">\n      <p>Autoptimize\'s Critical CSS speeds up your site by improving Google PageSpeed Insights performance indicators like <strong>\"first contentful paint\"</strong> and \"largest contentful paint\". Having the <strong>correct rules for each page</strong> is key to avoid \"cumulative layout shift\".</p>\n      <p><strong><a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize Pro</a> fully automates critical CSS rule creation</strong>, but also provides image optimization, CDN and extra powerful \"booster\" options all in one handy subscription to make your site even faster! See <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> for more info and maybe a discount code?</p>\n      <p>Alternatively with <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">criticalcss.com\'s 3EUR (4USD)/  month subscription</a> you can generate the right critical CSS for any given page and create manual rules yourself. You can also <strong>automate the entire process</strong> by opting for the \"WordPress\" plan (3EUR or 4USD subscription + 8EUR or 10USD per domain); simply <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">sign up</a>, copy/ paste <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">the API key</a> in the field below and Autoptimize will automatically start creating rules!</p>\n      <p>If you have any questions or need support, head on over to <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/autoptimize\" target=\"_blank\">our support forum</a> and we\'ll help you get up and running in no time!</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:28%;float:right\"><img src=\"https://criticalcss.com/images/criticalcss-optimised-website-illustration.svg\" width=\"350px\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'nl\'>\n    <h2>Verbeter de performantie van je site met critical CSS</h2>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden\">\n    <div style=\"width:68%;float:left\">\n      <p>De kritieke CSS van Autoptimize versnelt uw site door prestatie-indicatoren van PageSpeed Insights, zoals \'<strong>first contentful paint</strong>\' en \'<strong>largest contentful paint</strong>\', te verbeteren. De juiste \"kritieke CSS\"-regels voor elke pagina hebben, is essentieel om \"cumulative lay-out shift\" te voorkomen.</p>\n      <p><strong><a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize Pro</a> automatiseert het creëren van kritieke CSS regels volledig</strong>, maar optimaliseert ook uw afbeeldingen, biedt een CDN en bevat extra krachtige \"booster\" opties in 1 handig abonnement om uw site nog sneller te maken! Zie <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> voor meer info en misschien een kortingscode?</p>\n      <p>Als alternatief kunt u met <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">het abonnement van 2GBP/maand van criticalcss.com</a> voor elke pagina de juiste kritische CSS genereren en zelf handmatige regels maken. U kunt <strong>het hele proces ook automatiseren</strong> door te kiezen voor het \"WordPress\"-abonnement (2GBP abonnement + 5GBP per domein); <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">schrijf je in</a>, kopieer/plak <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">de API-sleutel</a> in het onderstaande veld en Autoptimize begint automatisch met het maken van regels!</p>\n      <p>Als je vragen hebt of ondersteuning nodig hebt, ga dan naar ons <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/autoptimize\" target=\"_blank\">support forum</a> en we helpen je snel aan de slag!</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:28%;float:right\"><img src=\"https://criticalcss.com/images/criticalcss-optimised-website-illustration.svg\" width=\"350px\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'fr\'> \n  <h2>Am&eacute;liorer la vitesse de votre site avec critical CSS</h2>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden\">\n    <div style=\"width:68%;float:left\">\n      <p>Le CSS critique d\'Autoptimize acc&eacute;l&egrave;re votre site en am&eacute;liorant les indicateurs de performance de PageSpeed Insights tels que \"<strong>premi&egrave;re peinture de contenu</strong>\" et \"<strong>plus grande peinture de contenu</strong>\". Avoir les r&egrave;gles correctes pour chaque page est essentiel pour &eacute;viter les \"changements de mise en page cumulatifs\".</p>\n      <p><strong><a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize Pro</a> vous aide &agrave; automatiser la cr&eacute;ation des r&egrave;gles de CSS critique</strong>, mais offre aussi l\'optimisation des images, CDN et des options extra \"booster\" tous dans un m&ecirc;me abonnement pour vous aider a am&eacute;liorer la vitesse de votre site! Voyez <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> pour plus d\'info et qui sait un code coupon?</p>\n      <p>Alternativement avec <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">l\'abonnement de 2GBP/mois de Criticalcss.com</a>, vous pouvez g&eacute;n&eacute;rer le bon CSS critique pour une page donn&eacute;e et cr&eacute;er vous-m&ecirc;me des r&egrave;gles manuelles. Vous pouvez &eacute;galement <strong>automatiser l\'ensemble du processus</strong> en optant pour le forfait \"WordPress\" (abonnement 2GBP + 5GBP par domaine) ; <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">inscrivez-vous</a>, copiez/collez <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">la cl&eacute; API</a> dans le champ ci-dessous et Autoptimize commencera automatiquement &agrave; cr&eacute;er des r&egrave;gles!</p>\n      <p>Si vous avez des questions ou si vous avez besoin d\'assistance, rendez-vous sur <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/autoptimize\" target=\"_blank\">notre forum d\'assistance</a> et nous vous aiderons &agrave; vous mettre en route en un rien de temps !</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:28%;float:right\"><img src=\"https://criticalcss.com/images/criticalcss-optimised-website-illustration.svg\" width=\"350px\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'pt\'>\n <h2>Melhore o desempenho do seu site com critical CSS</h2>\n  <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden\">\n  <div style=\"width:68%;float:left\">\n      <p>O CSS cr&iacute;tico do Autoptimize acelera seu site melhorando os indicadores de desempenho do PageSpeed Insights, como \"<strong>primeira pintura de conte&uacute;do</strong>\" e \"<strong>maior pintura de conte&uacute;do</strong>\". Ter as regras corretas para cada p&aacute;gina &eacute; fundamental para evitar \"mudan&ccedil;a cumulativa de layout\".</p>\n      <p>O <strong><a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize Pro</a></strong> automatiza totalmente a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de regras CSS cr&iacute;ticas, mas tamb&eacute;m fornece otimiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de imagem, CDN e op&ccedil;&otilde;es de &quot;booster&quot; extra poderosas, tudo em uma assinatura pr&aacute;tica para tornar seu site ainda mais r&aacute;pido! <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Veja https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> para mais informa&ccedil;&otilde;es e talvez um c&oacute;digo de desconto?</p>\n      <p>Alternativamente com a <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">assinatura de 2GBP/m&ecirc;s do criticalcss.com</a>, voc&ecirc; pode gerar o CSS cr&iacute;tico certo para qualquer p&aacute;gina e criar regras manuais por conta pr&oacute;pria. Voc&ecirc; tamb&eacute;m pode <strong>automatizar todo o processo</strong> optando pelo plano \"WordPress\" (assinatura de 2GBP + 5GBP por dom&iacute;nio); basta <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">se inscrever</a>, copiar/colar a <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">chave da API</a> no campo abaixo e o Autoptimize come&ccedil;ar&aacute; automaticamente a criar regras!</p>\n      <p>Se voc&ecirc; tem alguma d&uacute;vida ou precisa de suporte, v&aacute; ao <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/autoptimize\" target=\"_blank\">nosso f&oacute;rum de suporte</a> e n&oacute;s vamos ajud&aacute;-lo a colocar para funcionar em pouco tempo!</p>\n    </div>\n  	<div style=\"width:28%;float:right\"><img src=\"https://criticalcss.com/images/criticalcss-optimised-website-illustration.svg\" width=\"350px\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div> \n<div class=\'ao_i18n\' id=\'es\'>\n    <h2>Mejora el rendimiento de tu sitio con critical CSS</h2>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;overflow:hidden\">\n    <div style=\"width:68%;float:left\">\n      <p>El CSS cr&iacute;tico de Autoptimize acelera su sitio al mejorar los indicadores de rendimiento de Google PageSpeed Insights como \"<strong>primera pintura con contenido</strong>\" y \"<strong>la mayor pintura con contenido</strong>\". Tener las reglas correctas para cada p&aacute;gina es clave para evitar el \"cambio de dise&ntilde;o acumulativo\".</p>\n       fully automates critical CSS rule creation</strong>, but also provides image optimization, CDN and extra powerful \"booster\" options all in one handy subscription to make your site even faster! See https://autoptimize.com/pro/ for more info and maybe a discount code?</p>\n      <p><strong><a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize Pro</a></strong> automatiza por completo la creaci&oacute;n de reglas CSS cr&iacute;ticas, pero tambi&eacute;n proporciona optimizaci&oacute;n de im&aacute;genes, CDN y opciones de &quot;refuerzo&quot; extra potentes, &iexcl;todo en una pr&aacute;ctica suscripci&oacute;n para hacer que su sitio sea a&uacute;n m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido! Consulte <a href=\"https://autoptimize.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoptimize.com/pro/</a> para obtener m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n y tal vez un c&oacute;digo de descuento.</p>\n      <p>Alternativamente con la <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">suscripci&oacute;n mensual de 3 EUR (4 USD) de Criticalcss.com</a>, puede generar el CSS cr&iacute;tico adecuado para cualquier p&aacute;gina y crear reglas manuales usted mismo. Tambi&eacute;n puedes <strong>automatizar todo el proceso</strong> optando por el plan \"WordPress\" (3EUR o 4USD suscripci&oacute;n + 8EUR o 10USD por dominio); <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">simplemente reg&iacute;strese</a>, copie/pegue <a href=\"https://criticalcss.com/account/api-keys?aff=1\" target=\"_blank\">la clave API</a> en el campo a continuaci&oacute;n y Autoptimize comenzar&aacute; a crear reglas autom&aacute;ticamente.</p>\n      <p>Si tiene alguna pregunta o necesita asistencia, dir&iacute;jase a <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/autoptimize\" target=\"_blank\">nuestro foro de asistencia</a> y lo ayudaremos a ponerse en marcha en poco tiempo.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:28%;float:right\"><img src=\"https://criticalcss.com/images/criticalcss-optimised-website-illustration.svg\" width=\"350px\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n','no');
